13 An act relating to protecting the personal information of certain public
14 servants
15 It is hereby enacted by the General Assembly of the State of Vermont:
16 Sec. 1. FINDINGS AND PURPOSE
17 (a) The General Assembly finds that Vermont’s judges, prosecutors, law
18 enforcement officers, and other public servants play an essential role in the
19 functioning of the government of the State of Vermont and that the nature of
